Script,OpenInFourthSeat
setDealerCode(`

# Open In Fourth Seat

dealer west
produce 1000

Import,https://github.com/ADavidBailey/Practice-Bidding-Scenarios/blob/main/script/Calm-Opponents
# Defines calmOpps

# North passes
nPasses = hcp(north)<12 and shape(north,xxxx-any 7xxx-any 6xxx-any 55xx)

# South opens in fourth seat


# Rule of 15
r15 = hcp(south) + spades(south) and hcp(south)<13
sSouth = shape(south,any 64xx+any 63xx+any 54xx+any 53xx+any 4432+any 4333)

# North passes
nPasses = hcp(north)<12 and shape(north,xxxx-any 7xxx-any 6xxx-any 55xx)

sMightOpen = r15>13 and r15<17

Import,https://github.com/ADavidBailey/Practice-Bidding-Scenarios/blob/main/script/Level-the-Deal

levLow = r15<15
levEqual = r15==15
levHigh = r15>15
levelTheDeal = levLow or levEqual or levHigh

# Now do it
calmOpps and nPasses and sMightOpen
and levelTheDeal

action
average "HCP North=" hcp(north),
average "HCP South=" hcp(south),
frequency "r15   " (r15, 14,16),


`,"W",true)
Script
Button,4th Seat Opener,\n\
--- To Open or Not to Open\n\
After (P) P (P)...ï¼Œshould you open in 4th seat?\n\
%OpenInFourthSeat%
